            "title": "",
            "content": "<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">炽霞：难道只有厉害的残象漂泊者才能肉身吸收吗？</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">炽霞：或者需要是特定种类？</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">炽霞：还是&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p class=\"py-1 px-2 align-middle\">炽霞：要不然用终端试试？</p>\n</div>"
